          "name": "Kirtankumar Krishna Shetty",
          "email": "kirtan.shetty@seagate.com",
          "date": "2016-02-17 04:28:07.000000000",
          "tz": 330
        },
        "subject": "LU-7429 test: LFSCK isn't getting completed within given time.",
        "message": "LU-7429 test: LFSCK isn't getting completed within given time.\n\nThe test 23c of sanity-lfsck.sh times out after the specified time in\nwait_update not letting the LFSCK to recover the dangling name entry.\nThis causes the test to fail and it is evident from the logs that the\nLFSCK was under progress. Just added an extra parameter into the\nwait_update function that will accept the interval for checking the\nspecified condition for size of the file and also increased the time\nfor LFSCK to let it recover the dangling name entry.\n\nChange-Id: I2ccb8cfae03e84ce68ec9c7a142816c1b2bab8ee\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-3134\nSigned-off-by: Kirtankumar Krishna Shetty <kirtan.shetty@seagate.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
